OL,5, The UK faces its biggest fall in       
OL,6, spending power for 70 years as the     
OL,7, surging cost of living eats into       
OL,8, people's wages.                        
OL,10,FThe government's independent forecaster
OL,11,Fsaid that household incomes - once     
OL,12,Frising prices were taken into account -
OL,13,Fwould drop by 6% this year and next.   
OL,15,FLiving standards won't recover to      
OL,16,Fpre-pandemic levels until 2027, it     
OL,17,Fwarned.                                
OL,19,FIt came as Chancellor Jeremy Hunt said 
OL,20,Fthe economy would shrink this year but 
OL,21,Favoid recession.                       
